<font size=2><table width="100%" bgcolor="#004b97"><font color=#d2d200><b>Cloak of the Jharin Recruit</b></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=1><a style="color: #ffffff" href="mailto:jcsmith@amazinghideaways.com?subject=Regarding: Cloak of the Jharin Recruit">Submit Info</a></font></table>
<font color=white>

LORE 
NO DROP 



<br><br>


<b>Inventory Slots:</b> Back
<br>







<b>Armor Class:</b> 5<br>
<b>Modifiers:</b> Pottery +1%, Cha +2, HP +5<br>
<b>Size:</b> Medium<br>
<b>Weight:</b> 5<br>

<br>
<b>Classes:</b> BRD<br>
<b>Races:</b> VAH<br>





<br>




























<br><table width="300" bgcolor="#004b97"><b><font color=#d2d200>Obtained in 
<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqquestfull&eqquests.quest_name=%22Cloak%20of%20the%20Jharin%20Recruit%22">Cloak of the Jharin Recruit</a> Quest</b></font></table><br>
<b>Recommended Level:</b> 4<br>
<b>Starting NPC:</b> Gherik Alarhun<br><br>

<b>Description</b>:<br>
This is the second in the line of Shar Vahl bard quests. It requires your slate from the first quest. It requires some pottery skill.<BR><BR>1) Kill Whiptail Scorpions in the pit of Shar Vahl until you receive three shells.<BR><BR>2) Kill Xakra Larva in the pit until you receive Xakra Worm Larvae.<BR><BR>3) Kill Grimling Skeletons in the pit until you receive four Grimling Femur Bones.<BR><BR>4) Give the slate to Gherik Alarhun in Shar Vahl(+260,-510). <BR><BR>5) Give Gherik Alarhun your three scorpion shells. He will give you a container and a sketch.<BR><BR>6) Combine the four Grimling Femur Bones in to the container that Gherik gave you. This will create a powder.<BR><BR>7) Combine the Powder, Xakra Larvae, and Water in to the same container. This will create a Bile Clay.<BR><BR>8) Combine the Bile Clay, Sketch and Water with a Pottery Wheel. This will create an Unfired Bowl.<BR><BR>9) Give the Unfired Bowl to Gherik Alarhun. <BR><BR>10) Give your acrylia slate to Broker Fahaar in Shar Vahl(+230,-25). He will give you a container.<BR><BR>11) Kill Young Hoppers in the pit until you have four young hopper hides. <BR><BR>12) Combine the four young hopper hides in to your container. <BR><BR>13) Hand the resulting item to Broker Fahaar. He will give you a Leather Chord and a Stretched Hopper Hide.<BR><BR>14) Use a Kiln to Combine your Unfired Jharin Bowl, a Quality Firing Sheet and  Flask of Water. This will make a Bowl of Jharin.<BR><BR>15) Give your Initiate Cloak, Stretched Hopperhide, Leather Chord and Bowl of Jharin to Gherik Alarhun. He will give you a buckler.<BR><BR>16) Give the Buckler to Hymnist Gawfed in Shar Vahl. He will give you a receipt.<BR><BR>17) Give the Receipt to Jihli Mahej and he will give you give you a vase and send you to Chogar.<BR><BR>18) Give it to Chogar. He will give you a Sketch.<BR><BR>19) Combine the Sketch, Block of Clay and Quality Firing Sheet in a Pottery Wheel. This makes a vase.<BR><BR>20) Give vase to Hymnist Gawfed, recieve bag to fill with 7 feathers from owlbears and recruit cloak. Return to Gawfed.<br>


<br><table width="300" bgcolor="#004b97"><b><font color=#d2d200>Found in <a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqzone&eqzones.zone_name=%22Shar%20Vahl%22">Shar Vahl</a></b></font></table><br>
<b>Continent:</b> Luclin<br>
<b>Zone Type:</b> Town<br>
<b>Level Ranges:</b> 1 - 60<br>
<b>Connects To:</b> Hollowshade Moor, Shadeweaver's Thicket<br><br>

<b>Description:</b><br>This city of the Vah Shir is in the crater of a shard of Norrath that was blasted into Luclin when the hole was created.  The guilds are Bard, Beastlord, Rogue, Shaman and Warrior<br>




